<html>
<head>
<meta charset='UTF-8'>
<link rel="stylesheet" href="/static/cgi.css">
</head>
<body>
[% IF email %]
    <img src='https://akash.mountmadonna.org/static/images/mmc-teal.png' width=200>
[% ELSE %]
    <img src='/static/images/mmc-teal.png' width=200>
[% END %]
<p>
Thank you, ${first}.
[% IF amount %]
    <p>
    Your payment has been received.
[% END %]
<p>
[% IF title == 'Personal Retreat' %]
    [% IF mountain_experience %]
        We have received your online registration for a Mountain Experience
        on ${sdate.format("%A %B %e, %Y")}.
    [% ELSE %]
        We have received your online registration for a Personal Retreat
        from ${sdate.format("%A %B %e, %Y")} to ${edate.format("%A %B %e, %Y")}.
    [% END %]
[% ELSE %]
    We have received your online registration for the
    $title program[% IF leader_names %] with $leader_names[% END %]
    from ${sdate.format("%A %B %e, %Y")} to ${edate.format("%A %B %e, %Y")}.
[% END %]
[% IF amount %]
    <p>
    Your credit card has been charged \$${amount}.<br>
    The id for this transaction is ${transaction_id}.
[% END %]
<p>
[% IF ! email %]
The above information has been sent to you via an email to ${email}.<br>
[% END %]
You will soon receive <i>another</i> letter from programs@mountmadonna.org
with confirmation of your
[% IF mountain_experience || housing_not_needed %]
    registration.
[% ELSE %]
    housing and all the details you will need to know
    prior to coming to Mount Madonna Center.
[% END %]
<p>
If you do not receive this other letter within 3 days check your
spam/junk email folder.
If it is not there please call us at 408-846-4090.
[% IF ! housing_not_needed %]
    <p>
    Do <b>not</b> make travel plans until you have received
    your housing confirmation letter.
    <p>
    [% IF withwhom_last || withwhom_first %]
        <p>
        You requested to be housed with $withwhom_first ${withwhom_last}.
        They <b>MUST REGISTER SEPARATELY</b>.<br>
        [% IF pid == 0 %]
            <a href="https://www.mountmadonna.org/cgi-bin/regPR">Click here to go back to the registration page</a> and register them.</p>
        [% ELSE %]
            <a href="https://www.mountmadonna.org/cgi-bin/reg1?id=$pid">Click here to go back to the registration page</a> and register them.</p>
        [% END %]
    [% END %]
[% END %]
</body>
</html>
